-- Siemens Supports Nuclear Exit in Ad Campaign, Handelsblatt Says
-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 2012-03-09T06:32:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-09/siemens-supports-nuclear-exit-in-ad-campaign-handelsblatt-says.html
Siemens AG (SIE)  Chief Executive Officer
 Peter Loescher  is supporting  Germany ’s decision to exit nuclear
power in a forthcoming advertising campaign,  Handelsblatt 
newspaper reported today, without saying where it got the
information.  Germany’s energy transition could lead to new innovations
and increase exports of environmentally friendly technologies,
according to Loescher, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
 nmagnusson1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at 
 acullen8@bloomberg.net  